******
[2]
Date: 29 Dec 2010
Source: Bloomberg Business Week [summarised, edited]
<http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-12-29/s-korea-raises-foot-and-mouth-alert-to-highest-level.html>


The government has mobilized 172 348 quarantine personnel including
public servants, soldiers and the police for the decontamination and
culling process, the government said. Authorities plan to complete
limited vaccinations of animals ahead of schedule, it said.

[Byline: Sungwoo Park]

