[In archived post 20101228.4575, ProMED-mail requested clarification
on the seemingly large number (155 974) of "mobilized quarantine
personnel to man 1226 checkpoints across the country and to take part
in the decontamination and culling process." This issue has become
clearer thanks to item 2 above, according to which the engaged army
and police forces were included in the cited number. - Mod.AS]
